import { Label } from '@mui/icons-material';
import { Button, Container, Divider, FormControlLabel, FormGroup, List, ListItem, ListItemText, Stack, Switch, TextField } from '@mui/material';
import React, { useState } from 'react';


function CadastroPeixes(){
const[value,setValue]=useState();
const handleChange=e=>{
  console.log(`Form ${e.target.value}`)
}

 return (
    <Container display='flex'align-itens='center' >
    <div >
      <List>

        <Divider />

      <Stack spacing={2} direction='row'  >
        <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >

          <TextField

            label="PitTag"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
            value={value}
            onChange={handleChange}

          />

          <TextField

            label="Comprimento Padrão"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
            value={value}
            onChange={handleChange}
          />


          <TextField

            label="Local de Captura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
          />
          <TextField

            label="Data de Soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required />
          <TextField

            label="Código da Amostra de DNA"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required />
        </Stack>

        <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >

          <TextField

            label="Nome Científico da Espécie"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Comprimento total"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Peso na Soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Local da soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <FormGroup>
            <FormControlLabel label="Recaptura" control={<Switch defaultChecked />} />

          </FormGroup>
        </Stack>
      </Stack>
    </div >

    <div>
    <List>
      <ListItem >
        <ListItemText primary="Informações de Recaptura" />
      </ListItem>
      <Divider />
    </List>
    <Stack spacing={2} direction='row'   >
      <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >
       
        <TextField

          label="Comprimento total"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required

        />

        <TextField

          label="Peso na soltura"
          variant='outlined'

          required
        />


        <TextField

          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required
        />
        <TextField

          label="Recaptura"
          variant='outlined'
          color='primary'
          required />

      </Stack>

      <Stack direction='column' spacing={2}   >

        <TextField

          color='primary'

        />

          label="Data de Captura"

          variant='outlined'

          required

        />

        <Button size='small' variant='outlined' color='inherit' >Salvar</Button>
        
      </Stack>
    </Stack>
  </div >
</Container >
 );   
}
export default CadastroPeixes;
